Chala excellent doubt Hemanth 👌🔥
Idi adigithe ardham nuvvu concept deep ga alochistunnav. Idi Spring Boot lo very important internal process.

Nee doubt simple ga:

JSON pampincham → Java object ayyindi (Student s)
Kani method Student return chestundi → JSON response vachindi
Object enduku object ga raledu?

Answer: Spring Boot automatic ga conversion chestundi.

Dinini Serialization & Deserialization antaru.

🟢 Step-by-Step Flow
1️⃣ Postman Request

Postman nundi nuvvu pampinchindi:

{
"id":101,
"name":"prince",
"course":"SpringBoot"
}

Header:

Content-Type: application/json
2️⃣ Spring Boot receives JSON

Controller method:

@PostMapping("/add")
public Student addStudent(@RequestBody Student s) {
    return s;
}

@RequestBody meaning:

JSON → Java Object

Spring Boot internally chestundi:

Student s = new Student(101,"prince","SpringBoot");

This process = Deserialization

🟢 3️⃣ Method Execution

Method run ayindi:

return s;

Meaning:

return Student object

But HTTP response Java object pampinchalem.

HTTP lo pampinchagaligedi:

Text
JSON
XML
HTML

Kabatti Spring Boot convert chestundi.

🟢 4️⃣ Object → JSON Conversion

Spring Boot internally chestundi:

Student → JSON

Result:

{
"id":101,
"name":"prince",
"course":"SpringBoot"
}

This process = Serialization

🧠 Important Library

Spring Boot lo ee conversion Jackson library chestundi.

Dependency automatically add avuthundi:

spring-boot-starter-web

Jackson classes:

ObjectMapper
JsonSerializer
JsonDeserializer
🟢 Visual Flow

Complete request flow:

Postman
   ↓
JSON
   ↓
@RequestBody
   ↓
Student Object
   ↓
Controller Logic
   ↓
return Student
   ↓
Jackson
   ↓
JSON Response
   ↓
Postman
🟢 Short Rule
Direction	Conversion
JSON → Java Object	Deserialization
Java Object → JSON	Serialization
🧪 Example

If method return chesthe:

@GetMapping("/test")
public Student getStudent() {
    return new Student(1,"Hemanth","Spring");
}

Response automatically:

{
"id":1,
"name":"Hemanth",
"course":"Spring"
}
⭐ Real reason

Spring Boot detect chestundi:

@RestController

Meaning:

Return value = Response Body

So Spring automatically:

Object → JSON

convert chestundi.

🧠 Real Interview Question

How does Spring Boot convert Java objects to JSON?

Answer:

Spring Boot uses Jackson library to convert Java objects to JSON and JSON to Java objects automatically.
